		<div id="comment_body_65283887"><p>"No word for word copying is going on"</p><p>You don't know that. It can't keep a record of everything it's read, but the models are largely black boxes. There's really no way to know if it's memorizing long passages</p><p>The only way to test this would be to see if it generated identical passages. And these tools have indeed done so. It actually doesn't even matter if it's actually copying word for word or whether it's parallel construction. Its still infringement if it's the same words.</p></div>
