			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~n0w0rries">n0w0rries</a>  <span class="uid"><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~n0w0rries">( 832057 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_65283589"></span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65283589"><p>It's really simple. We have the technology.<br>Let AI read everything.<br>If you charge for AI, then you share the revenue you make off the knowledge you learned.<br>If you charge $10 for a response that includes information learned from 3 books written by John Doe, John Doe gets a % of what you charge.<br>Maybe your CEO doesn't get paid $100M a month as a result, I'm ok with that.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_65283589">

